Analyze Your Data

Salesforce Analytics Tools include Reports and Dashboards, Data Cloud Reports and Dashboards, CRM Analytics, and more.

Drill Deeper Into Data

You can drill deeper into your data to explore the underlying information and surface hidden insights. This is available in Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience, as well as Developer Edition.

To drill in:

* Select datapoints in a chart or rows in a table by clicking.
* Use multiple clicks or drag to select data.
* To deselect data, click again or click outside the selection box.

Open the Drill Into This By... menu by right-clicking or .

Select a dimension from the menu to view underlying data grouped and filtered. A new visualization will appear.

To return to previous views, click .
title: Drilling Deeper into Salesforce Data
